image_analysis.description: A vertical photograph showing a large object or architectural feature covered in translucent and black plastic sheeting. The object is positioned within a stone or masonry alcove or doorway. The stone blocks on either side are light-colored and rectangular. The plastic sheeting is draped over a tall, multi-pronged structure that appears to be a large menorah or a similar candelabra-style object. The top portion of the alcove is covered with black plastic, while the lower portion is covered with clear/translucent plastic.
